platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Quirky, fast-paced, and exhilarating, Golf Blitzs bite-size multiplayer battles play out on wild courses. Forget the etiquette of traditional golf: Activate power-ups and swing as quickly as possible to land ahead of the competition and even knock opponents off greens. The goal is to sink your ball first, so aim, swing, and shoot without delay in this brilliant supercharged interpretation of one of the worlds most contemplative sports.
